vendors.title: Cash Crazy
vendors.description:
Hold on to your seat and get ready for Cash Crazy.
This classic one line video slot has major winning combinations with Crazy Professor Wilds that multiply your winnings up to 4x. Get 3 Crazy Professor symbols on a win line to cash out the Jackpot!

vendors.title: Deuces And Joker
vendors.description:
You'll never play regular poker again with Deuces and Joker Multi.
This is Deuces and Joker on jet fuel with 4 hands played simultaneously. Just like Deuces and Joker all deuces are wild and an joker has been added as well. There's also a double up feature to further increase your winnings!

vendors.title: Double Double Bonus
vendors.description:
Double Double Bonus is is played without wild cards but with added pay out combinations and higher winnings.
This video poker game have added a total of 5 different combinations of four of a kind with staggering pay outs. If you like video poker then you're absolutely going to love this game!

vendors.title: Double Joker
vendors.description:
Double the fun, and your winnings with Double Joker.
This version of video poker is played with a 54 card deck where two jokers has been added as wild cards. You also have the option to double your winnings by picking a higher card than the dealer!

vendors.title: Germinator
vendors.description:
Get bitten by the bug in the fun arcade game Germinator.
In this arcade game you try to match three germs in a row, and more germs will fall down as you win. If you collect three pills you get to remove one type of germs for bigger winnings!

vendors.title: Harveys
vendors.description:
Dress up in your finest clothes for a night out in Harveys.
This video slot with a restaurant theme will leave you hungry for more, with its scatters and wilds. When the screen fills up with champagne you are taken to Free Spins where your winnings can be multiplied up to 25x!

vendors.title: Jacks Or Better
vendors.description:
Huge prizes waits for you if you can make the right decisions in Jacks or Better.
In this classic video poker game, you win with a pair of Jacks or better. Hit a royal flush and you will take home the ultimate win. Good luck on the field!

vendors.title: King Arthur
vendors.description:
Join the legendary Knights of the Round Table in King Arthur.
This epic video slot takes you on a medieval journey. It features wilds, 2x wilds, scatters and a bonus game. Big rewards awaits those who can pull the sword out of the stone!

vendors.title: Max Damage and The Alien Attack
vendors.description:
Explore space and fight against UFO's in Max Damage and The Alien Attack.
This awesome arcade game puts you in the seat of a space ship. You blast your way through waves of enemies to complete stages and progress to the next level. This is a truly unique game!
vendors.promo: Max Damage and The Alien Attack

vendors.title: Money Mad Monkey
vendors.description:
Go bananas in the fun video slot Money Mad Monkey.
This video slot has many features such as wilds, Free Spins and the bonus game Trail Climb. If you get three barrels you get to choose one of them for an instant money prize. This game has something for everyone!

vendors.title: Red Dog Progressive
vendors.description:
Red Dog is a old card game from the western times.
In this game you're handed 3 cards, one of them is covered though and you are to bet on the spread. Raise if you think it's a good chance that the covered card has a number inbetween the two shown cards. Good luck!

vendors.title: Sun Quest
vendors.description:
Brighten up your day at Sun Quest.
This is a colorful video slot with all the classic fruit symbols that you enjoy, combined with a touch of gold. It features 9 lines, wilds, scatter symbols and a Golden Sun Quest symbol which will pay out massive winnings!

vendors.title: Super Bonus Bingo
vendors.description:
Bingo has never been more fun than in Super Bonus Bingo.
Pick between 2-10 balls and watch 20 balls reveal themselves in the tube. If you hit all your numbers you will win an amazing 10 000x your stake. As a bonus feature you may also buy 2 additional balls at the end of the game!

vendors.title: The Codfather
vendors.description:
There is some fishy business going on in The Codfather.
This game features fantastic graphics and designs with a fishy theme. All winnings from wild symbols are doubled. Collect 3 Godfather scatters to enter the Free Spins mode.

vendors.title: Tiger Vs Bear
vendors.description:
See if the tiger or the bear wins the stand-off in Tiger vs Bear.
This video slot oiffers amazing graphics and music. It features wilds and two different bonus modes. The Tiger Bonus gives you Free Spins with stacked wilds and the Bear Bonus lets you pick your own rewards!

vendors.title: Tomb Raider 2
vendors.description: Time for another adventure in the video slot Tombraider II. This sequal of Tombraider offers you a lot of new features such as the Global Adventure Bonus Game, and Rolling Reels Free Spins where winnings reels are crushed and multipliers are added as you win!

vendors.title: Triple Chance Hilo
vendors.description:
Guess if the next card is going to be higher or lower in Triple Chance Hilo.
The difference between Triple Chance Hilo and normal Hilo games is that in this version you have three cards to choose from each round instead of just one. Show your skills and win big!

vendors.title: Triple Wins Star Ticket
vendors.description:
Pick your scratch tool and scratch a Triple Wins Star Ticket.
This scratch card is simple but entertaining. You pick one out of ten scratch cards and try to scratch three of the kind. No flashing lights or disturbing sounds in this game - just pure scratch fun!

vendors.title: Vikings Treasure
vendors.description:
""Vikings Treasure is a five reel, fifteen payline slot that offers coin denominations from 0.01 to 1.00.
The wild symbol in the game is the viking. If three or more scatter icons appear on the reels at the same time, the player will be awarded fifteen free spins."
